
                            The BoB Shop
                           Demo Version 0.9
                        (c) Brian Lloyd, 1994


The Bob Shop is a shareware sprite/bob bank editor for the Amos programming 
language. Features include a full set of drawing tools, pattern fills, VCR 
type playback of sprite/bob banks and variable zoom window.

Please send any questions or comments to 
